description:
Devi Lynn, aka "Spartica," has never wrestled in a
single
season match up. She has
one Tag Team match under her belt and 3 tournament
matches. She was 2-1 in
the Tournament and it can be said she is one of US's
elite wrestlers. She is
tough and tenacious, and she has skills and some
added college
wrestling experience.
Madison Young, aka "The Butcher," comes with some
experience too. Both her father and
brother were great wrestlers. Only time will tell if
she can make the
adjustment that so many others have struggled with.
title: Spartica(0-0) Not Ranked
